casebody.data:
Ann Fedak v. Joseph Woichowski, Executor (Estate of Walter M. Wojkowsky), et al.

Alcorn, C. J., House, Cotter, Thim and Ryan, Js.

Argued October 7 decided November 3, 1970 Henry J. Isaac, for the appellants (defendants). Raphael Korff, with whom, on the brief, was Edward J. Behwncik, for the appellee (plaintiff). Pee Cueiam.

The conclusions of the trial court are supported by the unattacked finding of subordinate facts.

There is no error.
